/ # Can I embed images and videos in a tweet?

/ Yes, you can improve your answers by embedding rich content. Here's how:

/ ## Links
/ URLs will be autolinked. This means you can just copy and paste any URL you'd like to link to into the tweet and it will be turned into a link.

/ If you want your URL to be displayed not with its link but with a different text, you can use this markdown syntax for links.

/ ```
/ You'll find additional information [in the docs](http://example.com). Please reach out if you have any more questions.
/ ```

/ ## Images
/ ```
/ ![Image](http://example.com/image.jpg)
/ ![Image](http://example.com/image.png)
/ ```
/ Any image source will work:
/ http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3684/9478750520_0cb9982b71.jpg

/ For some site like flickr the image url will also work
/ http://www.flickr.com/photos/jamesbrew/9478750520

/ ## Videos
/ Embed the link to the video as a URL. It will be transformed into a live video when it comes from Youtube, Vimeo, Wistia and more.

/ ```
/ ...some text.

/ [Steve Jobs' Commencement Address](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UF8uR6Z6KLc)

/ Some more text...
/ ```

/ http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UF8uR6Z6KLc
/ http://vimeo.com/70817051
/ http://home.wistia.com/medias/b0767e8ebb

/ ## Slides
/ You may embed slides from SlideShare, SlideRocket, SpeakerDeck the same way as a video.

/ ```
/ [Next steps of our onboarding process](https://speakerdeck.com/bipuldeb/seven-deadly-tricks-seven-ways-to-storytelling)
/ ```

/ https://speakerdeck.com/bipuldeb/seven-deadly-tricks-seven-ways-to-storytelling
/ http://slideshare.net/liubinskas/pollenizer-universal-pitch-deck
